</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
* [[Image:Draft_Wire.svg|32px]] [[Draft_Wire|Polyline]]: creates a polyline (also called wire), a sequence of several connected line segments.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
